  "text": "While the training data made available for the shared task consisted of both abstracts and full articles from the BioScope corpus [CITATION_1] , the test data were pre-announced to consist of biomedical articles only. In order to make the testing situation during development as similar as possible to what could be expected for the held-out testing, we only tested on sentences taken from the articles part of the training data. When developing the classifiers we performed 10-fold training and testing over the articles, while always including all sentences from the abstracts in the training set as well. Table 2 provides some basic descriptive figures summarizing the training data.",
